description._content: Description: Dam erected to converse water supply at half-way halt between Ganawah and Kiloo-Kerim. Location: Ganawah, Kiloo-Kerim, Persia Description: Motor Transport at Kiloo-Kerim, the Rest House on Ganawah_Mishun Road. Location: Ganawah, Kiloo-Kerim, Persia Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/714 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives.
